Remmina remote desktop client with FreeRDP 3.x (NLA + smartcard support).

# Remmina
Remmina is a remote desktop client that supports RDP, VNC, SSH, SPICE and more.
This build includes FreeRDP 3.24.0 with full NLA authentication (Kerberos/NTLM via CredSSP)
and smartcard passthrough support for RDP sessions.
